title: Aliens have landed on Earth and are living among us
subject: Conspiracy
text: Aliens have been secretly living among humans for decades, according to new evidence.

title: Chocolate cures all diseases, says new study
subject: Health
text: A recent study claims that consuming chocolate daily can cure almost any disease.

title: The moon is made of cheese, scientists confirm
subject: Science
text: A group of scientists has confirmed that the moon is, in fact, made entirely of cheese.
